{"published time": "2024-03-22T12:00:00+08:00", "images": ["https://socialistiskrevolution.files.wordpress.com/2024/03/billede-6.png?w=768", "https://socialistiskrevolution.files.wordpress.com/2024/03/3-768x510-1.jpg?w=768", "https://socialistiskrevolution.files.wordpress.com/2024/03/2-768x512-1.jpg?w=768", "https://socialistiskrevolution.files.wordpress.com/2024/03/4-2.jpg?w=683", "https://socialistiskrevolution.files.wordpress.com/2024/03/5-blur-768x527-1.webp?w=768", "https://socialistiskrevolution.files.wordpress.com/2024/03/6-blur-768x510-1.webp?w=768", "https://socialistiskrevolution.files.wordpress.com/2024/03/billede-7.png?w=768", "https://socialistiskrevolution.files.wordpress.com/2024/03/billede-8.png?w=768"], "content": "<div class=\"entry-content\"><p class=\"has-text-align-justify\"><em>Hereby we publish an unofficial translation of<a href=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/tribunal-popular-junco-maranhao/\">An article published</a>I a nova democracy (and).</em></p><figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-6809\" data-attachment-id=\"6809\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-meta='{\"aperture\":\"0\",\"credit\":\"\",\"camera\":\"\",\"caption\":\"\",\"created_timestamp\":\"0\",\"copyright\":\"\",\"focal_length\":\"0\",\"iso\":\"0\",\"shutter_speed\":\"0\",\"title\":\"\",\"orientation\":\"0\"}' data-image-title=\"billede-6\" data-large-file=\"https://socialistiskrevolution.files.wordpress.com/2024/03/billede-6.png?w=768\" data-medium-file=\"https://socialistiskrevolution.files.wordpress.com/2024/03/billede-6.png?w=300\" data-orig-file=\"https://socialistiskrevolution.files.wordpress.com/2024/03/billede-6.png\" data-orig-size=\"768,510\" data-permalink=\"https://socialistiskrevolution.wordpress.com/2024/03/22/brasilien-folkedomstolen-mod-jordberovelser-og-landbaserede-forbrydelser-afholdt-i-junco-do-maranhao/billede-6-13/\" height=\"510\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" src=\"../Images/2024-03-22T12-00-00-08-00/000000.png\" srcset=\"../Images/2024-03-22T12-00-00-08-00/000000.png\" width=\"768\"/></figure><p class=\"has-text-align-justify\">On March 9 and 10, the victorious People's Court against landscapes and land -based crimes were held in the village of Vilela in Junco Do Maranh\u00e3o. Here, popular lawyers, researchers, trade unionists and state journalists from other regions in the country participated in the court's judging committee.</p><p class=\"has-text-align-justify\">The Court also had the participation of various organizations, such as Uni\u00e3o Das Comunidades Em Luta and Coletivo Estudantil Filhos do Povo, who organized students to attend the event. The peasant leader<a href=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/ma-luiz-vila-nova-memorias-da-vida-e-da-luta-de-um-militante-foi-relancado-em-evento-na-ufma/\">Luiz Vila Nova</a>Also participated in the event.</p><figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped wp-block-gallery-1 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\" data-carousel-extra='{\"blog_id\":159656698,\"permalink\":\"https:\\/\\/socialistiskrevolution.wordpress.com\\/2024\\/03\\/22\\/brasilien-folkedomstolen-mod-jordberovelser-og-landbaserede-forbrydelser-afholdt-i-junco-do-maranhao\\/\"}'><figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-6812\" data-attachment-id=\"6812\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-id=\"6812\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-meta='{\"aperture\":\"0\",\"credit\":\"\",\"camera\":\"\",\"caption\":\"\",\"created_timestamp\":\"0\",\"copyright\":\"\",\"focal_length\":\"0\",\"iso\":\"0\",\"shutter_speed\":\"0\",\"title\":\"\",\"orientation\":\"0\"}' data-image-title=\"3-768\u00d7510-1\" data-large-file=\"https://socialistiskrevolution.files.wordpress.com/2024/03/3-768x510-1.jpg?w=768\" data-medium-file=\"https://socialistiskrevolution.files.wordpress.com/2024/03/3-768x510-1.jpg?w=300\" data-orig-file=\"https://socialistiskrevolution.files.wordpress.com/2024/03/3-768x510-1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"768,510\" data-permalink=\"https://socialistiskrevolution.wordpress.com/2024/03/22/brasilien-folkedomstolen-mod-jordberovelser-og-landbaserede-forbrydelser-afholdt-i-junco-do-maranhao/3-768x510-1/\" height=\"510\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" src=\"../Images/2024-03-22T12-00-00-08-00/000001.jpg\" srcset=\"../Images/2024-03-22T12-00-00-08-00/000001.jpg\" width=\"768\"/></figure><figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-6811\" data-attachment-id=\"6811\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-id=\"6811\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-meta='{\"aperture\":\"0\",\"credit\":\"\",\"camera\":\"\",\"caption\":\"\",\"created_timestamp\":\"0\",\"copyright\":\"\",\"focal_length\":\"0\",\"iso\":\"0\",\"shutter_speed\":\"0\",\"title\":\"\",\"orientation\":\"0\"}' data-image-title=\"2-768\u00d7512-1\" data-large-file=\"https://socialistiskrevolution.files.wordpress.com/2024/03/2-768x512-1.jpg?w=768\" data-medium-file=\"https://socialistiskrevolution.files.wordpress.com/2024/03/2-768x512-1.jpg?w=300\" data-orig-file=\"https://socialistiskrevolution.files.wordpress.com/2024/03/2-768x512-1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"768,512\" data-permalink=\"https://socialistiskrevolution.wordpress.com/2024/03/22/brasilien-folkedomstolen-mod-jordberovelser-og-landbaserede-forbrydelser-afholdt-i-junco-do-maranhao/2-768x512-1/\" height=\"512\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" src=\"../Images/2024-03-22T12-00-00-08-00/000002.jpg\" srcset=\"../Images/2024-03-22T12-00-00-08-00/000002.jpg\" width=\"768\"/></figure></figure><p class=\"has-text-align-justify\">Throughout the auditorium, the flags of the organization adorned the flags and banners with slogons about the struggle for the redistribution of land. Right at the access road hung a banner \u00bb<strong>Out with the earthenwork! For titulation of our belongings!</strong>\"The tone struck the event. Inside the auditorium there were other banners who condemned soil deprivations, mining on a large scale and called for peasant unit. The signatures came from occupiers from various communities such as Gleba Campina, Povoado Vilela, Caranandeua and Jaraquara communities and the peasant association Povoado de Maracacuera in Carutapera Municipality.</p><figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped wp-block-gallery-3 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\" data-carousel-extra='{\"blog_id\":159656698,\"permalink\":\"https:\\/\\/socialistiskrevolution.wordpress.com\\/2024\\/03\\/22\\/brasilien-folkedomstolen-mod-jordberovelser-og-landbaserede-forbrydelser-afholdt-i-junco-do-maranhao\\/\"}'><figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-6815\" data-attachment-id=\"6815\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-id=\"6815\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-meta='{\"aperture\":\"0\",\"credit\":\"\",\"camera\":\"\",\"caption\":\"\",\"created_timestamp\":\"0\",\"copyright\":\"\",\"focal_length\":\"0\",\"iso\":\"0\",\"shutter_speed\":\"0\",\"title\":\"\",\"orientation\":\"0\"}' data-image-title=\"4-2\" data-large-file=\"https://socialistiskrevolution.files.wordpress.com/2024/03/4-2.jpg?w=683\" data-medium-file=\"https://socialistiskrevolution.files.wordpress.com/2024/03/4-2.jpg?w=200\" data-orig-file=\"https://socialistiskrevolution.files.wordpress.com/2024/03/4-2.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"683,1024\" data-permalink=\"https://socialistiskrevolution.wordpress.com/2024/03/22/brasilien-folkedomstolen-mod-jordberovelser-og-landbaserede-forbrydelser-afholdt-i-junco-do-maranhao/4-2-8/\" height=\"1024\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 683px) 100vw, 683px\" src=\"../Images/2024-03-22T12-00-00-08-00/000003.jpg\" srcset=\"../Images/2024-03-22T12-00-00-08-00/000003.jpg\" width=\"683\"/></figure><figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-6816\" data-attachment-id=\"6816\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-id=\"6816\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-meta='{\"aperture\":\"0\",\"credit\":\"\",\"camera\":\"\",\"caption\":\"\",\"created_timestamp\":\"0\",\"copyright\":\"\",\"focal_length\":\"0\",\"iso\":\"0\",\"shutter_speed\":\"0\",\"title\":\"\",\"orientation\":\"0\"}' data-image-title=\"5-blur-768\u00d7527-1\" data-large-file=\"https://socialistiskrevolution.files.wordpress.com/2024/03/5-blur-768x527-1.webp?w=768\" data-medium-file=\"https://socialistiskrevolution.files.wordpress.com/2024/03/5-blur-768x527-1.webp?w=300\" data-orig-file=\"https://socialistiskrevolution.files.wordpress.com/2024/03/5-blur-768x527-1.webp\" data-orig-size=\"768,527\" data-permalink=\"https://socialistiskrevolution.wordpress.com/2024/03/22/brasilien-folkedomstolen-mod-jordberovelser-og-landbaserede-forbrydelser-afholdt-i-junco-do-maranhao/5-blur-768x527-1/\" height=\"527\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" src=\"../Images/2024-03-22T12-00-00-08-00/000004.png\" srcset=\"../Images/2024-03-22T12-00-00-08-00/000004.png\" width=\"768\"/></figure><figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-6814\" data-attachment-id=\"6814\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-id=\"6814\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-meta='{\"aperture\":\"0\",\"credit\":\"\",\"camera\":\"\",\"caption\":\"\",\"created_timestamp\":\"0\",\"copyright\":\"\",\"focal_length\":\"0\",\"iso\":\"0\",\"shutter_speed\":\"0\",\"title\":\"\",\"orientation\":\"0\"}' data-image-title=\"6-blur-768\u00d7510-1\" data-large-file=\"https://socialistiskrevolution.files.wordpress.com/2024/03/6-blur-768x510-1.webp?w=768\" data-medium-file=\"https://socialistiskrevolution.files.wordpress.com/2024/03/6-blur-768x510-1.webp?w=300\" data-orig-file=\"https://socialistiskrevolution.files.wordpress.com/2024/03/6-blur-768x510-1.webp\" data-orig-size=\"768,510\" data-permalink=\"https://socialistiskrevolution.wordpress.com/2024/03/22/brasilien-folkedomstolen-mod-jordberovelser-og-landbaserede-forbrydelser-afholdt-i-junco-do-maranhao/6-blur-768x510-1/\" height=\"510\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" src=\"../Images/2024-03-22T12-00-00-08-00/000005.png\" srcset=\"../Images/2024-03-22T12-00-00-08-00/000005.png\" width=\"768\"/></figure></figure><p class=\"has-text-align-justify\">In one of the activities of the event, the peasants organized a motorcycle caravan to visit Gleba Campina and investigate the crimes that the soils have committed there.</p><figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-6818\" data-attachment-id=\"6818\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-meta='{\"aperture\":\"0\",\"credit\":\"\",\"camera\":\"\",\"caption\":\"\",\"created_timestamp\":\"0\",\"copyright\":\"\",\"focal_length\":\"0\",\"iso\":\"0\",\"shutter_speed\":\"0\",\"title\":\"\",\"orientation\":\"0\"}' data-image-title=\"billede-7\" data-large-file=\"https://socialistiskrevolution.files.wordpress.com/2024/03/billede-7.png?w=768\" data-medium-file=\"https://socialistiskrevolution.files.wordpress.com/2024/03/billede-7.png?w=300\" data-orig-file=\"https://socialistiskrevolution.files.wordpress.com/2024/03/billede-7.png\" data-orig-size=\"768,510\" data-permalink=\"https://socialistiskrevolution.wordpress.com/2024/03/22/brasilien-folkedomstolen-mod-jordberovelser-og-landbaserede-forbrydelser-afholdt-i-junco-do-maranhao/billede-7-12/\" height=\"510\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" src=\"../Images/2024-03-22T12-00-00-08-00/000006.png\" srcset=\"../Images/2024-03-22T12-00-00-08-00/000006.png\" width=\"768\"/></figure><p class=\"has-text-align-justify\">As directed by the People's Court, the organizations present called for a day of mobilization and struggle against the State of Maranh\u00e3o's land deprivation law on May 1. The note can be read<a href=\"https://medium.com/@comsolute/nota-conjunta-abaixo-a-lei-da-grilagem-35783ca1efa7\">In its entirety here</a>.</p><p class=\"has-text-align-justify\">I en f\u00e6lles Note Skriver Solidarity Solidarity Committee for the Fight for the Land (Comfort) OG Union of Communities in Fighting (UCL):<em>\"This is a victorious event in every way: by establishing and reconciling a political agenda to defend the human rights of the population; by producing legal material in support of the communities of the local communities; by touching those present around solidarity with the struggle for soil '.</em></p><p class=\"has-text-align-justify\">The note also gives a warm greeting to Coletivo Estudantil Filhos do Povo, who had prepared a bus full of students. According to those present, the People's Court was a milestone in the development of the new student movement in Maranh\u00e3o.</p><figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-6820\" data-attachment-id=\"6820\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-meta='{\"aperture\":\"0\",\"credit\":\"\",\"camera\":\"\",\"caption\":\"\",\"created_timestamp\":\"0\",\"copyright\":\"\",\"focal_length\":\"0\",\"iso\":\"0\",\"shutter_speed\":\"0\",\"title\":\"\",\"orientation\":\"0\"}' data-image-title=\"billede-8\" data-large-file=\"https://socialistiskrevolution.files.wordpress.com/2024/03/billede-8.png?w=768\" data-medium-file=\"https://socialistiskrevolution.files.wordpress.com/2024/03/billede-8.png?w=300\" data-orig-file=\"https://socialistiskrevolution.files.wordpress.com/2024/03/billede-8.png\" data-orig-size=\"768,512\" data-permalink=\"https://socialistiskrevolution.wordpress.com/2024/03/22/brasilien-folkedomstolen-mod-jordberovelser-og-landbaserede-forbrydelser-afholdt-i-junco-do-maranhao/billede-8-12/\" height=\"512\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" src=\"../Images/2024-03-2